ygData.messageBody:
U dun see the point of forming one guild coz u create char in so many servers, and within same servers u also make several chars, hehehe.

But for those who is training only 1 or 2 chars in Innoruuk, forming our own guild means alot to us ;)

Ziltus Planeswalker
